name: Larissa #1
description: Larissa is a friend of a friend. I'd been living up in the hills on a farm and not shooting for way too long and constantly complaining about it so a friend took it upon herself to introduce Larissa and I specifically to shoot photos. Couldn't rally say no at that point and I'm glad I didn't. That's the creek behind my house. It's only running when there is snow melt so IT WAS COLD. She was a trooper though.
